Package js

Contains no specific set of classes; any classes in here are designed to be used individually throughout a program.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
JSActivityIndicator JSActivityIndicator allows a spinner to be displayed when invisible processing is occurring.
JSBadgeButton JSBadgeButton is an extension to JButton which allows an iOS style notification badge to be added to the button.
JSCalendar JSCalendar provides a simple way to display a calendar on screen and allows 'events' to be added and displayed.
JSConfirmDialogWithCheckbox Deprecated. JSConfirmDialogWithCheckbox has been deprecated because it's much easier and looks much nicer if you use JOptionPane.
JSDateEntry JSDateEntry provides a number of different ways for the user to enter a date.
JSDateUtil  
JSDialog An extension to JDialog which simply provides a way to animate size changes and to give the dialog a gradient as a background instead of a solid color.
JSFrame An extension to JFrame which provides a way to animate size changes and to give the frame a gradient as a background instead of a solid color.
JSGridPanel GridPanel is a type of JPanel.
JSLog JSLog is an extension of JSTextFileUtility which allows a simple "log" to be kept.
JSNotification JSNotification provides a way to display a small notification on screen with a title and short paragraph of text.
JSPanel JSPanel provides an easy way to give a JPanel a gradient as a background rather than a solid color.
JSPrintPreview JSPrintPreview provides a 'print preview' interface for printing a document using Java.
JSProgressBar An alternative to which has a consistent look across all platforms and is more customisable than JProgressBar.
JSProgressWindow A dialog which displays a progress bar and a message.
JSRoundButton An implementation of an iTunes style push button, which is a subclass of JButton.
JSStepper JSStepper is an alternative to JSpinner.
JSTable JSTable is a solution for creating a simple JTable.
JSTableDialog JSTableDialog is a class which allows a JSTable to be placed into a dialog along with a customisable set of JButtons.
JSTextField An extension to JTextField which provides a suggestion list and the ability to set a maximum entry length.
JSTextFileReader Deprecated. JSTextFileReader has been deprecated in favour of the more fully-featured JSTextFileUtility, which supports writing to a file as well as reading from it.
JSTextFileUtility JSTextFileUtility is a class which provides simple read/write access to a plain text file stored on disk.
JSUtil This class provides some useful time-saving methods, mostly for working with text.
 

Package js Description

Contains no specific set of classes; any classes in here are designed to be used individually throughout a program.
